------------------ regionalEffects ---------
Chilly fog lightly obscures the land within 6 miles of the dragon's lair.
Freezing precipitation falls within 6 miles of the dragon's lair, sometimes forming blizzard conditions when the dragon is at rest
Icy walls block off areas in the dragon's lair. Each wal is 6 inches thick, and a 10-ft section has AC 5, 15 hit points, vulnerability to fire damage, and immunity to acid, cold, necrotic, poison, and psychic damage. If the dragon wishes to move through a wall, it can do so without slowing down. The portion of the wall the dragon moves through is destroyed, however
